Tremonti Says Hasn’t Pressured Bank of Italy on Governor Choice

-- B y   J e f f r e y   D o n o v a n   a n d   L o r e n z o   T o t a r o
-- 
2011-10-19T08:09:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-19/tremonti-says-hasn-t-pressured-bank-of-italy-on-governor-choice.html
Italian Finance Minister  Giulio Tremonti  said he hadn’t put any pressure on the Bank of  Italy 
over the choice of a successor to Governor  Mario Draghi . He made
his comments in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
